<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3622] DCTDecode image with separation colorspace not rendered correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3622</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PDF reported by Ford Wang in the mailing list. The &quot;herbs&quot; have weird purple dots. The cause are DCTDecode (jpeg) images with a separation colorspace, e.g. &lt;tt&gt;Root/Pages/Kids/[0]/Resources/XObject/Im5267&lt;/tt&gt; . The image itself is a grayscale image, i.e. it has only one color component. The separation colorspace is a green (PANTONE 355 C), which is based on an Lab colorspace.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
